{{- define "wake_immediate_discovery" -}}
Urgent discoveries need immediate action:

1. Read discovered[] entries with urgency=immediate
2. For each, execute decision NOW:
   - Convert to task → execute liza_add_tasks tool NOW, then set converted_to_task=<new-task-id> via fallback state edit + liza_validate
   - Defer → set converted_to_task="deferred" with rationale via fallback state edit + liza_validate
   - Dismiss → set converted_to_task="dismissed" via fallback state edit + liza_validate
3. Prioritize new tasks appropriately (may be high priority)
4. Check if discoveries invalidate existing tasks — update them if needed
5. All discovered items must be processed and all tools executed in this session.
{{- end -}}
